        <updateDate>2004-05-03T20:20:54Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>COLA Fairness Act of 2004 - Requires the Bureau of Labor Statistics of the Department of Labor to establish, for 14 specified regions in the United States, monthly regional consumer price indices for computation of cost-of-living increases for Social Security and Medicare (title XVIII of the Social Security Act) benefits.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
